latestPosts.caption:
When we got married, Shubhankar dreamt of going to Padmanabh Swamy temple with me and I dreamt of going to Triyuginarayan temple with him. Extreme North & extreme South destinations, uniting on one pure emotion : Love. We feel so so so much blessed to be able to fulfill the dream of one of us to witness and seek blessings of the Padmanabha Swamy as husband and wife! Everything was so peaceful. The moment we saw the idol completely,( The idol is so huge that you’ve to take Darshan from 3 पठ moving right to left) we got so emotional and overwhelmed, simply smiling wide looking at each other. The ऊर्जा around can just be felt and not expressed through words. 2 days before visiting this temple, we saw a beautiful video of where Bhagwan Vishnu lives and how he is resting peacefully beyond this Universe and constantly Creating. When we saw the idol, it felt like here it is where Vishnu ji is truly resting and making his creations. Mann kiya ki doobara line me lag kar unhe phirse dekhne jau par fir jaana ki inhe dekh kar mann kabhi bhar hi nahi sakta iss zindagi mein. Every time I close my eyes since then, the first thing I can see is this most beautiful-huge-magical-highly energetic Murti of Sree Padmanabha. To us, this temple will always be the most precious in terms of its beauty, emotion, peace and love. 
Message from us - If you could, please visit this temple once in your lifetime. 
Jai Sree Padmanabha Swamy 😇🙏❤️✨🧿
May we fulfill my dream soon as well. 
Untill then, हर हर महादेव! 
.
